headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Hidden Cache Bonus
content: Intrepid treasure-hunters and seafarers who manage to scout the ocean floor for 10 Hidden Caches this week will get a reward to the tune of GTA$100,000 next week. Hop in an Avisa or Toreador, turn on your Sonar and get hunting. There's also scuba gear available in your Kosatka for those who prefer to get hands on.
